{"tid":1438993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［攬炒兄弟］今日新疆 明日香港","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:34:41.000Z","uid":278136,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff542e805d175369c26db619b54f5f7598289b8f","tid":1438993,"uid":278136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"去到依家，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地仲以為可以返轉頭咩？</span></span><br />\n唔好以為支共會放過我地，全香港已經處於同一命運<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日新疆 明日香港</span></span><br />\n呢個講法應該唔駛點解釋，只要我地一放棄，淨下嘅只係支共嘅清算，以及更進一步嘅蠶食，香港人將會被屠殺，或者被清洗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今次係最後嘅機會</span><br />\n難得今次事件已經引起全球共鳴，而香港亦成為中美貿易戰嘅其中一步棋，攬炒嘅力量有晒buff。<br />\n<br />\n去到依家，當你仲想講和<br />\n你就諗一諗：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支共會講諾言咩？說好嘅一國兩制五十年不變，二十五年就被收皮喇</span>"},{"pid":"1d46c5ce25aaba394b22781abde3e1678df00b99","tid":1438993,"uid":278136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"896f45eede54438c9dc17e40e432f08afb94f62e","tid":1438993,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"民間自衛隊 應該要出黎 阻止黑勢力 直到集會完結<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438977</a>"},{"pid":"fe7df74951340f815844aade7bffe493256fced6","tid":1438993,"uid":278136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"896f45eede54438c9dc17e40e432f08afb94f62e","tid":1438993,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"民間自衛隊 應該要出黎 阻止黑勢力 直到集會完結<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438977</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"若然佢地攪事<br />\n復仇閪 說要清算佢地業務<br />\n逐個地點舉報"},{"pid":"01e9334749125dd84210729df87a900e68beba19","tid":1438993,"uid":278136,